{
 "file": "_STGX4B.bin",
 "source_size": 37732,
 "built_size": 40352,
 "edits": [
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x13a1",
   "jp_len": 70,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "あいうえおかダチッツテ{01}デ、トドナ。つネハバパ·々ビブベミメちっぞャー（ルで·{00}！々、M合ぬな、{00}{01}！破{00}Mるにな、{00}{01}ぁ那是……！",
   "zh_hex": "15161718191a1b6566676869016a026b6c6d032e6f70717204077375777a7c2c2d297e080a82300400060702135c2d3302000106c70013042c3302000115e7b7e7b60909ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x140c",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那玩意儿、是什么东西？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e970ef3ceb7c02e7b6e7dde7bde8bae7f805000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1417",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "既不是MA、要说是MS又大得出奇……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8c4e7b5e7b6efa7ea9c02ef2ae7ede7b6efa7ef9ee8f1efa5e80aefbee9040909000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1432",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "到底是什么来头、况且{00}那张高达似的脸……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d7e9b4e7b6e7dde7bdd9e92e02e8d0e99900e7b7eac5e812ef2be944e7b4eb69090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1473",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "有台MS从那架高达型机体内部钻了出来{00}！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7cbea161314e88ae7b7e99de812ef2be977e7e4bce99accedc1e7baafd90006000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x14b0",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "正朝我们这边冲过来了！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3beaadefcce7bbe7b9e899e95eef36efcfe7baef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x14bf",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "拉米亚斯舰长、请应战！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c2e878e7d6e7c8e7d4ef3402e83ae873ef28ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x14f1",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "全员进入第1战斗配置！MS立即出击！",
   "zh_hex": "15efb4e849e892e891e940eff7ef28e7ffea34ea0eef97efa7ef9ee86be855efbee7ccef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1508",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们这就迎击敌方MS部队！",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbe7b9e7c5e931e7cce7e3efb1efa7ef9eef70e7c9ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x153d",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可恶、又出现了！没完没了！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7de02e8f1efbee82fe7baef97e7d8e87ee7d8e7baef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1575",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "先打倒本体！恐怕、就只有这一个办法了{00}！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef8be7f5e848efa6ef4fef97eb33e95802e7c5ef32e7cbe7b9efb6e828e8eae84ee7ba00ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15c3",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……给我站住！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e839efccec31e859ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x15f2",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bdef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1628",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那家伙是我的猎物！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7dfe7fde7b6efcce7b4ef81e99eef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x165d",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啧！别碍事！",
   "zh_hex": "15e9faef97e7e5e8c6efb8ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1691",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "喝啊啊！",
   "zh_hex": "15ec54e7c3e7c3ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x172a",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什、什么……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dd02e7dde7bd09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1762",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "竟徒手把MS砸碎了……那家伙、到底是{00}何方神圣！？",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2ceb02aee81b1314efecebe0e7ba0909e7b7e7dfe7fd02e7d7e9b4e7b6008ad0e9aae90d06050000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17a3",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是恶魔高达！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6e7dee8d8e812ef2bef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17ad",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这里就是你的葬身之地！这一次、我定要{00}打倒你！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9ef31e7c5e7b6e7b8e7b4ee96e88de7cdef63ef97e7b9efb6e86402efcce867ef2a00e7f5e848e7b8ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x17cc",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "出来！高达啊……",
   "zh_hex": "15efbeefcfef97e812ef2be7c309090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x186c",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你这愚不可及的蠢货！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b9e959e7b5e7c4e9cfe7b4e94beaf5ef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18a7",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "咦！又冒出个奇怪的家伙……！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef49ef97e8f1eb7fefbee828e904ea07e7b4e7dfe7fd0909ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x18df",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你现身了啊！东方不败·亚洲尊者！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e82fe88de7bae7c306e8bad0e7b5e88f04e7d6eacdeccdad0606000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x190e",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这么轻易就放出机动武斗士、这就是你的{00}拳之道吗、多蒙！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7bde990e964e7c5e86cafe7e4ef30e8ece7ffa502e7b9e7c5e7b6e7b8e7b400ea65e7cde82ae80202e7e9e942060500000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x192e",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你既是我的弟子、就用自己的拳头打一场{00}给我看！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e8c4e7b6efcce7b4eb84e88602e7c5efb3efb5e8c9e7b4ea65e92ee7f5efb6e87600e839efcce7f6ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1966",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "吵死了！",
   "zh_hex": "15ec51ef6ae7baef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1971",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "投靠恶魔高达的你、根本不配当我的师父{00}！",
   "zh_hex": "15e948e8c7e7dee8d8e812ef2be7b4e7b802e9b8efa6e7b5ea34ef53efcce7b4e96ce88800ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x198b",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "如今你已是我的敌人！{00}东方不败·亚洲尊者！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f0a2e7b8ef3ae7b68be7b4e7e3b40600e8bad0e7b5e88f04e7d6eacdeccdad0606000000000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19c0",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可笑！弟子岂有胜过师父之理！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4ea1cef97eb84e886eac3e7cbe8dbef36e96ce888e7cde872ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19da",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "也好……你既然把话说到这份上、我就用{00}机动武斗士来奉陪你！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c0e7c70909e7b8e8c4e7efe81be81fe7ede7d7e7b9ea22ef4c02efcce7c5efb300e7e4ef30e8ece7ffef64efcfeac1ef42e7b8ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x19fc",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "现身吧、尊者高达！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e82fe88de7d002eccdef6ee812ef2bef97ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a31",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "求之不得！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e93ae7cde7b5e80aef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a3d",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "出来吧！高达啊啊——！！",
   "zh_hex": "15efbeefcfe7d0ef97e812ef2be7c3e7c3ebafebafef97ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a74",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "上吧、东方不败！！",
   "zh_hex": "15ef4ce7d002e8baefb1e7b5e88fef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1a81",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "高达格斗——！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e812ef2be824e7ffebafebafef97ef9700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ab8",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "预备……",
   "zh_hex": "15ea5ae87709090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1afd",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『『开始——！！』』",
   "zh_hex": "150c0ce7fae908ebafebafef97ef970d0d000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1b63",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "夸张得没空吐槽了……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8dfeac5e80ae7d8e93fedf2ee43e7ba09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1bd6",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "舰长、有通信！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d4ef3402e7cbef59e90fef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c27",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……舰长！！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7d4ef34ef97ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c56",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……咦？",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef49050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1c5d",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊、啊啊、是通信啊",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c302e7c3e7c302e7b6ef59e90fe7c3000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ca3",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……抱歉、多蒙又先冲出去了……",
   "zh_hex": "150909e922e92702e7e9e942e8f1b8e95eafe7ebe7ba090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1cda",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那个……请问您是？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e8280909e83ae997e835e7b605000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d00",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我叫深村玲",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce8c1eb0deb8eeee400000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d0b",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在那边战斗的那位、名叫多蒙·卡修",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29e7b7e899ef28e7ffe7b4e7b7e83402e8ace8c1e7e9e942ef4be801e9b000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d23",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们是为追击恶魔高达、奉新日本之命派{00}遣而来的",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbe7b6e7c1e8dde7cce7dee8d8e812ef2b02eac1ef8ae98aefa6e7cde853e98500edc0e89cefcfe7b4000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d5e",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这么说、那台高达是新日本殖民地开发的{00}？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7bde7ed02e7b7ea16e812ef2be7b6ef8ae98aefa6e8a9ef38ef63e7fae870e7b4000500000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1d94",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "它原名叫终极高达、是多蒙的父亲{00}开发的、",
   "zh_hex": "15e978e8e4e8ace8c1e8e2eacae812ef2b02e7b6e7e9e942e7b4e888e89400e7fae870e7b402000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1db5",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "却引发了暴走事故……",
   "zh_hex": "15eadfe9d0e870e7baea4fe890efb8ea090909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1de2",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "于是、就派遣了你们前来……",
   "zh_hex": "15e879e7b602e7c5e985edc0e7bae7b8e7bbef51efcf090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1df6",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……我明白了",
   "zh_hex": "150909efccef39e809e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e01",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "确实不能放任那样凶恶的高达不管啊",
   "zh_hex": "15e88ce87fe7b5e7c6e86ce89ae7b7e7daecb2e7dee7b4e812ef2be7b5e93be7c300000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e20",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们就齐心协力、把它制服吧",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbe7c5e924e82de8f6efb002e81be978e8dee9f1e7d00000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e4b",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "多谢您",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e9e8b2e835000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e7a",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "多蒙、刚才听到了吗！？这些人愿意帮我{00}们呢！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e9e94202e8bce836e8d1e7d7e7bae802ef9705e7b9e8a4efb2e961ef3ce910efcc00e7bbe907ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1e99",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "所以、你也一起协力吧……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7fbe7f302e7b8e7c0efb6e847e8f6efb0e7d009090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ec2",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "用不着！区区恶魔高达、我一个人就够了{00}！",
   "zh_hex": "15efb3e7b5e86def97ef35ef35e7dee8d8e812ef2b02efccefb6e828efb2e7c5e920e7ba00ef9700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ef4",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "多蒙！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e9e942ef97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1efc",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "对手可不止恶魔高达、你的师父他也在场{00}啊！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7beef66e7c4e7b5e869e7dee8d8e812ef2b02e7b8e7b4e96ce888e80ce7c0ef29e87600e7c3ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f36",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那家伙、根本不是我的师父……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7dfe7fd02e9b8efa6e7b5e7b6efcce7b4e96ce8880909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f62",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你总不能同时对付恶魔高达和尊者高达吧{00}！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e881e7b5e7c6e85def2de7bee97ee7dee8d8e812ef2be7d3eccdef6ee812ef2be7d000ef97050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1f9d",
   "jp_len": 6,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1fbe",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "别犟了、多蒙！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e5e6afe7ba02e7e9e942ef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1fea",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……好吧",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c7e7d0000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x1ff4",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过、把话说在前头、{00}可别拖我后腿啊！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef3602e81be81fe7edef29bae92e0200e7c4e7e5ec1b8be7feee91e7c3060500000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2033",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嘛、那我就尽力而为吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e93602e7b7efcce7c5e8f2efb0e89ce7c1e7d00000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x208d",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么！？那家伙……竟在自我再生！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bdef9705e7b7e7dfe7fd0909ef2cef29efb5efcce80bef8def97ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20ca",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "恶魔高达具备自我再生的机能！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dee8d8e812ef2bea14e877efb5efcce80bef8de7b4e7e4e7c6ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x20e1",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "想打倒它、就得一口气给它造成重创！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e6e7f5e848e97802e7c5e80aefb6eabde8ede839e978e93ee837e8a1e893ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2123",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "光是零零散散地攻击、只会任它不断再生{00}！",
   "zh_hex": "15e83de7b6eb74eb74ef68ef68ef63ef67e7cc02ef32e7e2e89ae978e7b5e982e80bef8d00ef97000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x213d",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "集中火力、一举击破它！",
   "zh_hex": "15ea98c0e8dada0287ea21e7ccc7e978060000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x217f",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可恶！它又再生了！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7deef97e978e8f1e80bef8de7baef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2191",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "但只要持续给它造成伤害……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dbef32ef2ae9efe9ade839e978e93ee837e8f9e9880909ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x21fd",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……逃了！？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8c2e7baef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x225a",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那、那样的怪物……真打得倒吗！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b702e7b7e7dae7b4ea07e99e0909e820e7f5e80ae848e802ef9705000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2296",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哼！你这……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b306e7b8e7b909090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x22e8",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你这大蠢货——！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b9efa5e94beaf5ebafebafef97ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2318",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊呀！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c3e9c6ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x233c",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "未战先慌、算什么！",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b4ef28ef8beb0502e889e7dde7bdef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2350",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那样岂不等于一开始就去认输！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7daeac3e7b5e826e879efb6e7fae908e7c5e7ebe8a0e8b9ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2384",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "队、队长……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c902e7c9ef3409090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x23a8",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "怎么了、巴尼！倒是回话啊！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f2e7bde7ba02e85be896ef97e848e7b6ef52e81fe7c3ef9705000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x23d6",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊、不、队长、刚才那个……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c302e7b502e7c9ef3402e8bce836e7b7e82809090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x23e5",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那颜色也……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7ec41e89fe7c00909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x240e",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我在问你呢、怎么不回话、巴尼！",
   "zh_hex": "15efccef29e997e7b8e90702e7f2e7bde7b5ef52e81f02e85be896ef97000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2442",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是！怀、怀兹曼伍长、明白了！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6ef97eb0302eb03e856e874ec07ef3402ef39e809e7baef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2470",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "敌人再怎么强大、终究也不过是机器！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e3efb2e80be7f2e7bde8adefa502e8e2e906e7c0e7b5ef36e7b6e7e4e8c3ef970000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2487",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "没有毁不掉的道理！集中火力、一举打倒{00}它！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d8e7cbe97ce7b5e9d3e7b4e82ae87206ea98c0e8dada0287ea21e7f5e84800e978060000000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x24c1",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是、是……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b602e7b60909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x24f7",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔……",
   "zh_hex": "15e81d09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x24fe",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "没想到竟被人抢了先……那家伙、有点本{00}事",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d8e7e6e7d7ef2ce7f1efb2ebc8e7baef8b0909e7b7e7dfe7fd02e7cbe822efa600efb8000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x253b",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可恶！明明恶魔高达就在眼前……！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7deef97ef39ef39e7dee8d8e812ef2be7c5ef29e90bef510909ef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x255b",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过、干脆退兵也是兵法之一！这一战、{00}就留待来日再决！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef3602e8d3edafe880ef93e7c0e7b6ef93e84ee7cdefb6ef97e7b9efb6ef280200e7c5e98ceaa8efcfe98ae80be8abef970000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x25aa",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "敌机、已全部击破！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e3e7e402ef3aefb4ef70e7ccef6def97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x25d4",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "恶魔高达吗……啧、还真是个不得了的家{00}伙！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dee8d8e812ef2be8020909e9fa02e7f7e820e7b6e828e7b5e80ae7bae7b4e7df00e7fdef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x260e",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "新日本殖民地的多蒙·卡修啊……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef8ae98aefa6e8a9ef38ef63e7b4e7e9e942ef4be801e9b0e7c309090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2623",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "刚才打得真漂亮",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bce836e7f5e80ae820ead0eaa20000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2634",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你那台MS、也是新日本制造的吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b7ea16efa7ef9e02e7c0e7b6ef8ae98aefa6e8dee93ee7b4e8020500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x268a",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "真是的、多蒙这个人！！怎么这么不近人{00}情！",
   "zh_hex": "15e820e7b6e7b402e7e9e942e7b9e828efb2ef97ef97e7f2e7bde7b9e7bde7b5efd8efb200e88bef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x269f",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……嗯、那是新日本开发的神高达",
   "zh_hex": "150909e86502e7b7e7b6ef8ae98ad2e7fae870e7b4e9aae812ef2b0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x26bf",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "准确说来、它不是MS、而是MF",
   "zh_hex": "15e87ae88ce7edefcf02e978e7b5e7b6efa7ef9e02e89ce7b6efa7eca50000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x26ef",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "MF……机动、武斗士？跟MS有什么不{00}一样吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15efa7eca50909e7e4ef3002e8ece7ffef6405e973efa7ef9ee7cbe7dde7bde7b500efb6e7dae80205000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2725",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "机动武斗士、是以出战高达格斗为前提打{00}造的机体",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e4ef30e8ece7ffef6402e7b6e7f3efbeef28e812ef2be824e7ffe7c1ef51e821e7f500e93ee7b4e7e4ef4f00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2760",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "机动武斗士、高达格斗……尽是些没听过{00}的词呢",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e4ef30e8ece7ffef6402e812ef2be824e7ff0909e8f2e7b6e8a4e7d8e8d1ef3600e7b4ec3de90700000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2799",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "所谓的高达格斗、是指……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7fbe92be7b4e812ef2be824e7ff02e7b6e8c00909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x27ab",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是各殖民地之间举办的、由机动武斗士彼{00}此对决的竞技大会",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e819e8a9ef38ef63e7cde8fcea21e8eae7b402e8a6e7e4ef30e8ece7ffef64efc900e7cae7bee8abe7b4eb11ea64efa5e7e20000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x27cc",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过、神高达是为了对付恶魔高达而特别{00}强化过的",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef3602e9aae812ef2be7b6e7c1e7bae7bee97ee7dee8d8e812ef2be89ce7cfe7e500e8ade9a5ef36e7b4000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2809",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、你们就是开着那台神高达、追踪{00}恶魔高达的吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e7b8e7bbe7c5e7b6e7fae86de7b7ea16e9aae812ef2b02e8ddec9700e7dee8d8e812ef2be7b4e7d005000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2843",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……正是如此",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef3be7b6e7f0e7ca000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2868",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那、你们今后……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b702e7b8e7bbefb9e7fe0909050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2894",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们本打算继续追踪恶魔高达……",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbefa6e7f5e889e9d6e9ade8ddec97e7dee8d8e812ef2b0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x28ae",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……可以的话、能否让我们与各位同行呢{00}？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c4e7f3e7b4e81f02e7c6e9bbe7f9efcce7bbe832e819e834e85defd6e9070005000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2905",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "喂、玲……！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bd02eee40909ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x292d",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可以的话、希望你能说说缘由……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7f3e7b4e81f02e87be965e7b8e7c6e7ede7edecf9e8a6090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2960",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "其实、方才那次也是如此……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8cfe87f02efb1e836e7b7e864e7c0e7b6e7f0e7ca0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x296e",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "看来、恶魔高达似乎总会出现在有强力{00}MS的地方",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f6efcf02e7dee8d8e812ef2be944e933e881e7e2efbee82fef29e7cbe8adefb000efa7ef9ee7b4ef63efb10000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x29a9",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这么说、它出现在我们面前、也是因为这{00}个？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7bde7ed02e978efbee82fef29efcce7bbe862ef5102e7c0e7b6ef33e7c1e7b900e82805000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x29d5",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……嗯、多半是的",
   "zh_hex": "150909e86502e7e9eadee7b6e7b40000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x29df",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "恶魔高达具备自我再生、自我增殖、自我{00}进化这3大机能",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dee8d8e812ef2bea14e877efb5efcce80bef8d02efb5efccea3de8a902efb5efcc00e892e9a5e7b9ef60efa5e7e4e7c6000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a03",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这只是推测、不过恶魔高达降临地球之后{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9ef32e7b6eaabeace02e7b5ef36e7dee8d8e812ef2be943ed1ebf95e7cde7fe00090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a1d",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "它似乎是靠吞并其他MS、来实现自我增{00}殖的",
   "zh_hex": "15e978e944e933e7b6e8c7ed32e957e8cfe80cefa7ef9e02efcfe87fe82fefb5efccea3d00e8a9e7b4000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a59",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "也就是说、越是强力的MS就越会被它盯{00}上吗",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c0e7c5e7b6e7ed02ea57e7b6e8adefb0e7b4efa7ef9ee7c5ea57e7e2e7f1e978eb9500ef4ce8020000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2a75",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "真是被个麻烦的家伙给盯上了啊",
   "zh_hex": "15e820e7b6e7f1e828ea36e95be7b4e7dfe7fde839eb95ef4ce7bae7c300000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2aa5",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "正因如此、我们才想与各位同行……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3bef33e7f0e7ca02efcce7bbe836e7e6e832e819e834e85defd6090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ad9",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我看没什么不可以的、隼人舰长？",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7f6e7d8e7dde7bde7b5e7c4e7f3e7b402ea35efb2e7d4ef3405000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2aec",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "反正都被盯上了、有他们同行反倒更让人{00}安心",
   "zh_hex": "15e87cef3be840e7f1eb95ef4ce7ba02e7cbe80ce7bbe85defd6e87ce848e952e7f9efb200e7fce82d000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b2e",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "再说、那样危险的机体、也总不能放着不{00}管啊",
   "zh_hex": "15e80be7ed02e7b7e7dae935e932e7b4e7e4ef4f02e7c0e881e7b5e7c6e86ce86de7b500e93be7c30000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b74",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是啊",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6e7c30000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2b7d",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你是叫多蒙、还有玲吧……今后就拜托你{00}们了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b6e8c1e7e9e94202e7f7e7cbeee4e7d00909efb9e7fee7c5e91ae7f4e7b800e7bbe7ba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2bb0",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "多谢您",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e9e8b2e835000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2bd5",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我叫多蒙·卡修……请多关照",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce8c1e7e9e942ef4be801e9b00909e83ae7e9e8bbea1a000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2bfc",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "新日本殖民地的多蒙·卡修啊……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef8ae98aefa6e8a9ef38ef63e7b4e7e9e942ef4be801e9b0e7c309090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2c11",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "刚才打得真漂亮",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bce836e7f5e80ae820ead0eaa20000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2c22",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你那台MS、也是新日本制造的吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b7ea16efa7ef9e02e7c0e7b6ef8ae98aefa6e8dee93ee7b4e8020500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2c78",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "真是的、多蒙这个人！！怎么这么不近人{00}情！",
   "zh_hex": "15e820e7b6e7b402e7e9e942e7b9e828efb2ef97ef97e7f2e7bde7b9e7bde7b5efd8efb200e88bef97000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2c8d",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……嗯、那是新日本开发的神高达",
   "zh_hex": "150909e86502e7b7e7b6ef8ae98ad2e7fae870e7b4e9aae812ef2b0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2cad",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "准确说来、它不是MS、而是MF",
   "zh_hex": "15e87ae88ce7edefcf02e978e7b5e7b6efa7ef9e02e89ce7b6efa7eca500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2cdd",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "MF……机动、武斗士？跟MS有什么不{00}一样吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15efa7eca50909e7e4ef3002e8ece7ffef6405e973efa7ef9ee7cbe7dde7bde7b500efb6e7dae80205000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2d13",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那台机体、是高达格斗专用的吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7ea16e7e4ef4f02e7b6e812ef2be824e7ffeb4befb3e7b4e7d0000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2d49",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你知道这些吗、施泰纳大尉？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e85ae82ae7b9e8a4e80202eb8deaeae882be860500000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2d7b",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不嫌弃的话、就由我来为各位说明吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ee0be938e7b4e81f02e7c5e8a6efccefcfe7c1e819e834e7edef39e7d0000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2dbd",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……队长？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c9ef34050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2dea",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "所谓高达格斗、要追溯到数年之前……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7fbe92be812ef2be824e7ff02ef2ae8ddee57e7d7e914e909e7cdef5109090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2e04",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是为了解决各殖民地之间的纷争而创立的",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e7c1e7bae89de8abe819e8a9ef38ef63e7cde8fce7b4ecf8e852e89ce893e86be7b400000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2e24",
   "jp_len": 40,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "每4年一届、让各方代表选手搭乘{00}名为高达的机体、",
   "zh_hex": "15ec25ea9be90987ee1202e7f9e819d0e8e7e9e7e966aeeb09ebb100e8ace7c1e812ef2be7b4e7e4bc02000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2e4c",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "称之为格斗、",
   "zh_hex": "15ea01e7cde7c1e824e7ff020000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2e80",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "相互交战、",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b1e9f9e861ef28020000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2eb9",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "彼此交战、",
   "zh_hex": "15efc9e7cae861ef28020000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ef2",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "拼到最后、胜出的高达之国、便握有主导{00}权",
   "zh_hex": "15ea66e7d7e8c5e7fe02e8dbefbee7b4e812ef2be7cdefc402e8faeb37e7cbe954ea4b00eb390000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2f38",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "您……真懂行呢……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8350909e820e8b09fe9070909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2f6e",
   "jp_len": 12,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嘛……毕竟是工作需要",
   "zh_hex": "15e9360909ea2cef2ce7b6eae4ef2fe92def2a000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2f9b",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "（工作？）",
   "zh_hex": "150aeae4ef2f050b0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2fca",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "啊、嗯……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c302e86509090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2fd4",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "总之、这台神高达、也是高达格斗专用的{00}机体",
   "zh_hex": "15e881e7cd02e7b9ea16e9aae812ef2b02e7c0e7b6e812ef2be824e7ffeb4bd8e7b400e7e4bc00000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x2ff3",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过、它已经为对付恶魔高达而强化过了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef3602e978ef3ae8b7e7c1e7bee97ee7dee8d8e812ef2be89ce8ade9a5ef36e7ba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3026",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "原、原来如此……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8e402e8e4efcfe7f0e7ca09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x302f",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、你们就是开着那台神高达、追踪{00}恶魔高达的吧？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e7b8e7bbe7c5e7b6e7fae86de7b7ea16e9aae812ef2b02e8ddec9700e7dee8d8e812ef2be7b4e7d005000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3069",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……正是如此",
   "zh_hex": "150909ef3be7b6e7f0e7ca000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x308e",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、你们接下来打算怎么办呢……？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e7b8e7bbefceef4defcfe7f5e889e7f2e7bde8eae90709090500000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x30c5",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们本打算继续追踪恶魔高达……",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbefa6e7f5e889e9d6e9ade8ddec97e7dee8d8e812ef2b0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x30df",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……可以的话、能否让我们与各位同行呢{00}？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c4e7f3e7b4e81f02e7c6e9bbe7f9efcce7bbe832e819e834e85defd6e90700050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3136",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "喂、玲……！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e8bd02eee40909ef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x315e",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "可以的话、希望你能说说缘由……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c4e7f3e7b4e81f02e87be965e7b8e7c6e7ede7edecf9e8a60909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x318e",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "其实、方才那次也是如此……",
   "zh_hex": "15e8cfe87f02efb1e836e7b7e864e7c0e7b6e7f0e7ca0909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x319c",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "看来、恶魔高达似乎总会出现在有强力{00}MS的地方",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f6efcf02e7dee8d8e812ef2be944e933e881e7e2efbee82fef29e7cbe8adefb000efa7ef9ee7b4ef63efb10000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x31d7",
   "jp_len": 17,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这么说、它出现在我们面前、也是因为这{00}个？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e7bde7ed02e978efbee82fef29efcce7bbe862ef5102e7c0e7b6ef33e7c1e7b900e82805000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3203",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……嗯、多半是的",
   "zh_hex": "150909e86502e7e9eadee7b6e7b4000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x320d",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "恶魔高达具备自我再生、自我增殖、自我{00}进化这3大机能",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dee8d8e812ef2bea14e877efb5efcce80bef8d02efb5efccea3de8a902efb5efcc00e892e9a5e7b9ef60efa5e7e4e7c6000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3231",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这只是推测、不过恶魔高达降临地球之后{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9ef32e7b6eaabeace02e7b5ef36e7dee8d8e812ef2be943ed1ebf95e7cde7fe00090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x324b",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "它似乎是靠吞并其他MS、来实现自我增{00}殖的",
   "zh_hex": "15e978e944e933e7b6e8c7ed32e957e8cfe80cefa7ef9e02efcfe87fe82fefb5efccea3d00e8a9e7b400000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3287",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "也就是说、越是强力的MS就越会被它盯{00}上",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c0e7c5e7b6e7ed02ea57e7b6e8adefb0e7b4efa7ef9ee7c5ea57e7e2e7f1e978eb9500ef4c00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x32a3",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "真是被个麻烦的家伙给盯上了啊",
   "zh_hex": "15e820e7b6e7f1e828ea36e95be7b4e7dfe7fde839eb95ef4ce7bae7c300000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x32d3",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "正因如此、我们才想与各位同行……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef3bef33e7f0e7ca02efcce7bbe836e7e6e832e819e834e85defd6090900000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3307",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我看没什么不可以的、隼人舰长？",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7f6e7d8e7dde7bde7b5e7c4e7f3e7b402ea35efb2e7d4ef3405000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x331a",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "反正都被盯上了、有他们同行反倒更让人{00}安心",
   "zh_hex": "15e87cef3be840e7f1eb95ef4ce7ba02e7cbe80ce7bbe85defd6e87ce848e952e7f9efb200e7fce82d000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x335c",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "再说、那样危险的机体、也总不能放着不{00}管啊",
   "zh_hex": "15e80be7ed02e7b7e7dae935e932e7b4e7e4ef4f02e7c0e881e7b5e7c6e86ce86de7b500e93be7c30000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x33a2",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是啊",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6e7c30000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x33ab",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你是叫多蒙、还有玲吧……今后就拜托你{00}们了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7b6e8c1e7e9e94202e7f7e7cbeee4e7d00909efb9e7fee7c5e91ae7f4e7b800e7bbe7ba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x33de",
   "jp_len": 10,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "多谢您",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e9e8b2e835000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3403",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我叫多蒙·卡修……请多关照",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce8c1e7e9e942ef4be801e9b00909e83ae7e9e8bbea1a000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x342a",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "哦……这就是神高达吗",
   "zh_hex": "15e9190909e7b9e7c5e7b6e9aae812ef2be802000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x343d",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "细看之下、不少细节都和MS大不一样啊",
   "zh_hex": "15eb9ae7f6e7cdef4d02e7b5efaceb9aebece840e7d3efa7ef9eefa5e7b5efb6e7dae7c3000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3473",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嚯……光是驾驶舱一带、就几乎是另一种{00}东西了",
   "zh_hex": "15e9dd0909e83de7b6e953e975ebebefb6e93702e7c5eaa5e933e7b6e99befb6e7d100e8bae7f8e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x34aa",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这叫机动追踪系统、能把搭乘者的动作直{00}接传给机体",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e8c1e7e4ef30e8ddec97e941e92902e7c6e81beb09ebb1ef6ee7b4ef30ef2fe87500efceea38e839e7e4ef4f0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x34e5",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、神高达那套乱来的动作、都是多蒙{00}那家伙弄出来的？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e9aae812ef2be7b7eb30e976d9e7b4ef30ef2f02e840e7b6e7e9e94200e7b7e7dfe7fdeac4afd9e7b4050000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3523",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……嗯",
   "zh_hex": "150909e8650000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x352a",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "能入选高达格斗的、大多是他那样的武道{00}家",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c6e891e966e812ef2be824e7ffe7b402bee7e9e7b6e80ce7b7e7dae7b4e8ece82a00e7df0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3567",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "寻常人就驾驭不了吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15efe2efc7efb2e7c5e953edcae7b5e7bae802050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3598",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "而且、这台机体还搭载了超级模式……",
   "zh_hex": "15e89ce99902e7b9ea16e7e4ef4fe7f7eb09eb1de7baeaf6eaeeea91ea260909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x35b4",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是即便在武斗士当中、也唯有多蒙才能{00}驾驭的机能",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6e855e8faef29e8ece7ffef64ef53ef4e02e7c0ea89e7cbe7e9e942e836e7c600e953edcae7b4e7e4e7c60000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x35ec",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "超级模式、就是刚才那闪着金光的玩意儿{00}？",
   "zh_hex": "15eaf6eaeeea91ea2602e7c5e7b6e8bce836e7b7ea44e86de902e83de7b4e970ef3ceb7c0005000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x361e",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "它通过反馈搭乘者强烈的情感、来激发出{00}机体的潜能",
   "zh_hex": "15e978ef59ef36e87ceecaeb09ebb1ef6ee8adeaece7b4e88be87d02efcfe9b9e870efbe00e7e4ef4fe7b4eb3ce7c60000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x365a",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "情感…",
   "zh_hex": "15e88be87d090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3662",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "若是卡缪、说不定也能驾驭得了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e7e7b6e801e91702e7ede7b5e867e7c0e7c6e953edcae80ae7ba00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3697",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "？卡缪是谁？",
   "zh_hex": "1505e801e917e7b6e9230500000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x36c1",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是之前加入奥古的一名驾驶员、如今正在{00}宇宙",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e7cdef51e854e891e82be84de7b4efb6e8ace953e975e84902e7f0efb9ef3bef2900e8bee8bf000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x36d9",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "作为NT确实出众、只是情感太过激烈了{00}些",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2fe7c1eed3eed6e88ce87fefbeeafb02ef32e7b6e88be87de86aef36e9b9eaece7ba00e8a40000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x36f5",
   "jp_len": 35,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "再加上他好像练过空手道、我才想说没准{00}合适……",
   "zh_hex": "15e80be854b2e80ce7c7e8e9eb13ef36e93faee82a028be836e7e6e7ede7d8e87a00a0ef410909000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3733",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是啊……那样的人、说不定还真挺合适的",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e7c30909e7b7e7dae7b4efb202e7ede7b5e867e7f7e820eb5cefc0ef41e7b40000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x374b",
   "jp_len": 41,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "或许还会放声狂笑、自称是『世界霸者』{00}什么的呢",
   "zh_hex": "15e905e8a7e7f7e7e2e86cea8aebd9ea1c02efb5ea01e7b60ce83ce8f5eefdef6e0d00e7dde7bde7b4e9070000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3795",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "若是那样、卡利乌斯曹长好像也挺合适",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e7e7b6e7b7e7da02e801e82ee94de7c8ed74ef34e7c7e8e9e7c0eb5ca0ef410000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x37ce",
   "jp_len": 11,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……什么呀",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7dde7bde9c60000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x37f0",
   "jp_len": 7,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b709090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x37f7",
   "jp_len": 29,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "虽说是意外耽搁了一阵、也差不多该前往{00}奥布了",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b8e7ede7b6ef3ce8f7eda7ed6ae7baefb6eb4802e7c0e9c7e7b5e7e9e898ef51e91100e82be831e7ba000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x382f",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……是啊",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b6e7c30000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x3838",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "OZ动向也令人在意、越早越好",
   "zh_hex": "15ed1ceedaef30efc1e7c0e94eefb2ef29ef3c02ea57e963ea57e7c7000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x38a1",
   "jp_len": 9,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……嗯？",
   "zh_hex": "150909e86505000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8016",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "竟、竟然就到此为止了吗……",
   "zh_hex": "15ef2c02ef2ce7efe7c5e7d7e7cae7c1e869e7bae80209090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8056",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……隼人舰长！民兵发来救援请求！",
   "zh_hex": "150909ea35b4e7d4ef3406ef38cee870d9e8cae863e83ae93a060000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8089",
   "jp_len": 8,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "什么！？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dde7bdef97050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x80ac",
   "jp_len": 20,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "看来、他们正与迪安娜回归军交战",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f6efcf02e80ce7bbef3be832ea11e7fce7eaef52e947e7e0e861ef28000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x80db",
   "jp_len": 18,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那个……所谓的民兵、是指什么？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e8280909e7fbe92be7b4ef38ef9302e7b6e8c0e7dde7bd050000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8108",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "是与卡拉巴合作的组织之一、由民间自发{00}组建的军事部队",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b6e832e801e7c2e85befc0ef2fe7b4ea0deb3fe7cdefb602e8a6ef38e8fcefb5e87000ea0dea61e7b4e7e0efb8ef70e7c90000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8144",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "记得、好像听说哪个财团组建了大规模的{00}自警团……",
   "zh_hex": "15e996e80a02e7c7e8e9e8d1e7ede8ffe828eea3ea5eea0dea61e7baefa5ea42ea91e7b400efb5eb6eea5e09090000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8180",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "你说的是莱因福德财团吧",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b8e7ede7b4e7b6e846ef33ea7ce82ceea3ea5ee7d0000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x818e",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我们和它的所有者古恩阁下、结成了相互{00}支援的合作关系",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce7bbe7d3e978e7b4e7fbe7cbef6ee84de7eee8d7ef4d02e868e837e7bae8b1e9f900e883e863e7b4efc0ef2fe8bbe9410000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x81c8",
   "jp_len": 23,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "既然如此、那就有必要前去救援了",
   "zh_hex": "15e8c4e7efe7f0e7ca02e7b7e7c5e7cbe860ef2aef51e7ebe8cae863e7ba0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x81df",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "拉米亚斯舰长、可以吗？",
   "zh_hex": "15e7c2e878e7d6e7c8e7d4ef3402e7c4e7f3e802050000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8208",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "嗯、没有异议",
   "zh_hex": "15e86502e7d8e7cbeb32e8e30000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8231",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那么、从现在起、我们{00}就前去救援民兵！",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7bd02e88ae82fef29e847028be7bb00e7c5bae7ebe8cae863ef38ce06000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x82ae",
   "jp_len": 13,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "一路辛苦了",
   "zh_hex": "15efb6e8d2ea58e9e6e7ba0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x82bb",
   "jp_len": 32,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "感谢你将这条『宇宙世纪路线』一路玩到{00}了最后",
   "zh_hex": "15e87de8b2e7b8e84ae7b9e9d40ce8bee8bfe83ceb99e8d2e9160defb6e8d2e970e7d700e7bae8c5e7fe0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x82db",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "另外、隆德·贝尔队的战斗、就在此暂告{00}一段落……",
   "zh_hex": "15e99be8f702ed16e82cef4be857e7e1e7c9e7b4ef28e7ff02e7c5ef29e7cae9ffe8e500efb6ea6be92a090900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x82fa",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过、游戏本身仍可继续、今后也请你尽{00}情享受",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef3602ea94ea3eefa6e88deab9e7c4e9d6e9ad02efb9e7fee7c0e83ae7b8e8f200e88bec06e8c80000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x831f",
   "jp_len": 39,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "另外、为通关本路线的你、还准备了特别{00}关卡",
   "zh_hex": "15e99be8f702e7c1ef59e8bbefa6e8d2e916e7b4e7b802e7f7e87ae877e7bae7cfe7e500e8bbe80100000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8346",
   "jp_len": 33,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是与另行奋战至今的大天使队进行的特{00}别演习",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6e832e99befd6ef46ef28e897efb9e7b4efa5e844e83fe7c9e892efd6e7b4e7cf00e7e5ea2feab600000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8367",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "和他们一战、检验一下你亲手培养的部队{00}实力、也不错",
   "zh_hex": "15e7d3e80ce7bbefb6ef2802ee40ea99efb6ef4de7b8e894ef66edfeec0be7b4ef70e7c900e87fefb002e7c0e7b5e8850000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x838c",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在自由对战中选择『特殊演习』、便可与{00}他们一战",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29efb5e8a6e7beef28ef4ee966eaaa0ce7cfed7bea2feab60d02e8fae7c4e83200e80ce7bbefb6ef280000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x83b1",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、『SD高达G世代DS』",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd020cef9eef96e812ef2beed1e83ce8e7ef96ef9e0d0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x83d5",
   "jp_len": 21,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "今后也请你尽情游玩到最后",
   "zh_hex": "15efb9e7fee7c0e83ae7b8e8f2e88bea94e970e7d7e8c5e7fe0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x844e",
   "jp_len": 31,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "谢谢你、一直陪着我这个不可靠的舰长",
   "zh_hex": "15e8b2e8b2e7b802efb6e875ef42e86defcce7b9e828e7b5e7c4e8c7e7b4e7d4ef3400000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x846d",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这条『平成高达路线』就到此结束了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e9d40ce887e837e812ef2be8d2e9160de7c5e7d7e7cae868e895e7ba00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x848b",
   "jp_len": 26,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过、虽然我们预防者的战斗已经结束…{00}…",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef3602e8b8e7efefcce7bbea5ae968ef6ee7b4ef28e7ffef3ae8b7e868e895090009000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x84a5",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……游戏本身仍可继续、今后也请继续享受",
   "zh_hex": "150909ea94ea3ed2e88deab9e7c4e9d6e9ad02a2e7fee7c0e83ae9d6e9adec06e8c800000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x84cb",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "还为通关这条路线的你、准备了新的关卡{00}哦",
   "zh_hex": "15e7f7e7c1ef59e8bbe7b9e9d4e8d2e916e7b4e7b802e87ae877e7baef8ae7b4e8bbe80100e91900000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x84ef",
   "jp_len": 27,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "那是与曾经和提坦斯、新吉翁交战的……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b7e7b6e832ea2ae8b7e7d3e821e843e7c802ef8ae7d9ee88e861ef28e7b40909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x850a",
   "jp_len": 19,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……隆德·贝尔队进行的特别演习哦",
   "zh_hex": "150909ed16e82cef4be857e7e1e7c9e892efd6e7b4e7cfe7e5ea2feab6e9190000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x851d",
   "jp_len": 38,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "在自由对战中选择『特别演习』、就能和{00}他们交战",
   "zh_hex": "15ef29efb5e8a6e7beef28ef4ee966eaaa0ce7cfe7e5ea2feab60d02e7c5e7c6e7d300e80ce7bbe861ef2800000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8543",
   "jp_len": 14,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "请一定要来挑战看看哦",
   "zh_hex": "15e83aefb6e867ef2aefcfeae7ef28e7f6e7f6e919000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8551",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、『SD高达G世代DS』",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd020cef9eef96e812ef2beed1e83ce8e7ef96ef9e0d0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8575",
   "jp_len": 28,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "『自由对战的战火！冲过去吧、大天使号{00}！！』",
   "zh_hex": "150cefb5e8a6e7beef28e7b4ef28e8daef97e95eef36e7ebe7d002efa5e844e83fe83300ef97ef970d0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x85f6",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我是主天使号舰长、娜塔尔·巴基露露{00}中佐",
   "zh_hex": "158be7b6e954e844e83fe833e7d4ef3402e7eae945e7e104e85be829e858e85800c0a300000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8606",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "首先、要向你一路以来出色的指挥、致以{00}敬意",
   "zh_hex": "15ef40b802ef2a9de7b887e8d2e7f3d9afe89fe7b4e8c0e94902ea32e7f300ee38ef3c00000000000000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8628",
   "jp_len": 34,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "多亏有你的协助、我们才得以奋战到了最{00}后",
   "zh_hex": "15e7e9eab7e7cbe7b8e7b4e8f6ea2302efcce7bbe836e80ae7f3ef46ef28e7d7e7bae8c500e7fe000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x864a",
   "jp_len": 22,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "这条『对手路线』就到此结束了",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b9e9d40ce7beef66e8d2e9160de7c5e7d7e7cae868e895e7ba0000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8660",
   "jp_len": 25,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "不过、虽然我们主天使队的战斗已经结束{00}……",
   "zh_hex": "15e7b5ef3602e8b8e7efefcce7bbe954e844e83fe7c9e7b4ef28e7ffef3ae8b7e868e895000909000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8679",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "但游戏本身仍可继续、今后也请你尽情享{00}受",
   "zh_hex": "15e7dbea94ea3eefa6e88deab9e7c4e9d6e9ad02efb9e7fee7c0e83ae7b8e8f2e88bec0600e8c8000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x869d",
   "jp_len": 43,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "自由对战今后仍可继续、此外、只要选择{00}『特别演习』……",
   "zh_hex": "15efb5e8a6e7beef28efb9e7feeab9e7c4e9d6e9ad02e7cae8f702ef32ef2ae966eaaa000ce7cfe7e5ea2feab60d09090000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x86c8",
   "jp_len": 30,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "便能与隆德·贝尔、预防者进行联合演习",
   "zh_hex": "15e8fae7c6e832ed16e82cef4be857e7e102ea5ae968ef6ee892efd6ef2eefc0ea2feab60000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x86e6",
   "jp_len": 37,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "我相信、与他们一战、你也必定能够取胜",
   "zh_hex": "15efcce8b1e90f02e832e80ce7bbefb6ef2802e7b8e7c0e860e867e7c6e920e987e8db0000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x870b",
   "jp_len": 36,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……那么、『SD高达G世代DS』",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7b7e7bd020cef9eef96e812ef2beed1e83ce8e7ef96ef9e0d0000000000000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x872f",
   "jp_len": 16,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "今后也祝你武运长久",
   "zh_hex": "15efb9e7fee7c0ed97e7b8e8ece986ef34e9db00000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8756",
   "jp_len": 15,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "唔！恶魔高达它……！！",
   "zh_hex": "15e81def97e7dee8d8e812ef2be9780909ef97ef9700000000"
  },
  {
   "jp_offset": "0x8765",
   "jp_len": 24,
   "kind": "dialogue",
   "zh_text": "……可恶！这场胜负、{00}就留待来日再决！！",
   "zh_hex": "150909e7c4e7de06e7b9e876e8dbe92c0200e7c5e98ceaa8d9e98ae80be8ab06060000000000000000"
  }
 ]
}
